There are a lot of government-related archive sites on the Internet,
many with public-domain images. NASA and JPL are good resources for
these.  The following WWW URL gives a list of astronomy-related
sites with pix.  You will need to verify the legalities for usage
of the images with each invidual site.  This list is several web-screens
long, BTW.

