Subject: RE: Setting up Imagine on PC
Date:    Thu, 20 Apr 1995 12:10:25 
From:    jkee@motown.ge.com

device=c:\dos\himem.sys
buffers=10,0
files=20
dos=umb
lastdrive=k
fcbs=16,0
devicehigh=c:\dos\setver.exe
stacks=9,256

lh /l:1,27248 c:\expert\mouse
PATH
C:\DOS;C:\;C:\PKWARE;D:\SCAN;C:\S64\UTIL;D:\XTG;C:\EXPERT;c:\dta;c:\disp
c:
set temp=f:\temp
cd \imag
imagine

  These are my autoexec.bat and config.sys files.
  They work good for me without any crashes or conflicts.

            Jon

