account. The mail server had been down for a whole week and they reactivated 
it on Fri, afternoon after 17:00, so I had gone home all the mail started 
coming in until my mailbox was full. :(

Now I'm ofcourse missing a whole bunch of messages and since I'm doing the 
archiving for the IML I would like to place a call for HELP.

Does somebody have mail archive (any form will do) starting around march 15 
upto Apr 22.

Please, Please send it to me: Joop.vandeWege@medew.ento.wau.nl
