software packages that I have to see how they would do something. Then I 
try to use that info to create the effect that I wantin imagine. What all 
this leads up to is I have a book called "3D Studio Special Effects" by New 
Riders Publishing. In it there is a tutorial on making a glass of water 
w/ ice cubes. The ice has the effect that you guys are looking for. I 
haven't done this one yet but will in the next couple of days to see how 
it was done then I'll try it in imagine. I'll let ya'll know how it turns 
