Hello Conny, on Apr 28 you wrote:

RB> > I have'nt investigated your problem with realistic fluids but as far as
> > glass goes, have you considered trying a Global Brushmap to bring out the
> > reflections in your glass.  I've had good results with chrome and glass
> > when combined with a quality brushmap, particularly one with a variety of
