Its already there 'cept its not called mirror! :) Well, I tell a lie, 
there is a bodgey way to do it quickly.... Select the transform menu. 
This will bring up a box where you can enter numbers to do things like 
scaling and rotation (just in case you haven't seen it yet). Then all you 
have to do is scale it LOCALLY on the axis you want to mirror (probably X 
in your case) by -1

